[
  {
    "startTime": 0.16,
    "endTime": 3.04,
    "text": "no one likes making their bed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.04,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "let alone washing their sheets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 8.88,
    "text": "especially single men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.88,
    "endTime": 12.24,
    "text": "in one survey 55 of single men between"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.24,
    "endTime": 15.04,
    "text": "18 and 25 reported changing their sheets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.04,
    "endTime": 18.16,
    "text": "only 4 times a year"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.16,
    "endTime": 19.68,
    "text": "and to be clear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.68,
    "endTime": 21.76,
    "text": "those are beds that you would not want"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.76,
    "endTime": 24.32,
    "text": "to sleep in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.84,
    "endTime": 28.24,
    "text": "you shed about 15 million skin cells"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.24,
    "endTime": 29.599,
    "text": "each night"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.599,
    "endTime": 31.039,
    "text": "but they don't just pile up in your"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.039,
    "endTime": 32.16,
    "text": "sheets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.16,
    "endTime": 34.96,
    "text": "because something else is already there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.96,
    "endTime": 38.239,
    "text": "waiting to gobble them up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.239,
    "endTime": 39.84,
    "text": "dust mites"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.84,
    "endTime": 42.239,
    "text": "and the longer you wait between washes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.239,
    "endTime": 44.8,
    "text": "the more food these critters will have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.8,
    "endTime": 47.039,
    "text": "and the more they'll procreate and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.039,
    "endTime": 48.559,
    "text": "multiply"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.559,
    "endTime": 50.64,
    "text": "so if you don't wash your sheets you'll"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.64,
    "endTime": 52.719,
    "text": "be sleeping with hundreds of thousands"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.719,
    "endTime": 54.64,
    "text": "of arachnids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.64,
    "endTime": 56.64,
    "text": "now for the estimated 20 million"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.64,
    "endTime": 58.879,
    "text": "americans with dust allergies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.879,
    "endTime": 60.879,
    "text": "it gets worse"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.879,
    "endTime": 62.48,
    "text": "dust mites and their feces produce"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.48,
    "endTime": 64.799,
    "text": "proteins that cause red and itchy eyes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.799,
    "endTime": 67.04,
    "text": "runny noses and other cold-like symptoms"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.04,
    "endTime": 69.28,
    "text": "in people who are allergic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.28,
    "endTime": 72.24,
    "text": "and dust mites well they're actually not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.24,
    "endTime": 75.119,
    "text": "the only allergen in a dirty bed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.119,
    "endTime": 77.36,
    "text": "if you never wash your pillow sheets a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.36,
    "endTime": 79.439,
    "text": "community of fungus can also build up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.439,
    "endTime": 80.64,
    "text": "there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.64,
    "endTime": 82.72,
    "text": "one study found that a typical pillow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.72,
    "endTime": 85.28,
    "text": "has as many as 16 different species of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.28,
    "endTime": 87.92,
    "text": "fungus and literally millions of fungal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.92,
    "endTime": 89.439,
    "text": "spores"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.439,
    "endTime": 91.119,
    "text": "and the most common among them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.119,
    "endTime": 93.68,
    "text": "aspergillus fumigatus is potentially"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.68,
    "endTime": 95.28,
    "text": "dangerous"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.28,
    "endTime": 97.6,
    "text": "in addition to allergic reactions it can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.6,
    "endTime": 100.4,
    "text": "infect your lungs and other organs and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.4,
    "endTime": 103.28,
    "text": "it's not just fungi joining the party"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.28,
    "endTime": 105.68,
    "text": "you see bacteria also love a good"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.68,
    "endTime": 107.759,
    "text": "unwashed pillow case or sheet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.759,
    "endTime": 109.28,
    "text": "a lot"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.28,
    "endTime": 111.2,
    "text": "another study found that unwashed pillow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.2,
    "endTime": 114.079,
    "text": "cases and sheets had up to 39 times more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.079,
    "endTime": 116.64,
    "text": "bacteria than pet food bowls"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.64,
    "endTime": 119.2,
    "text": "and several thousand times more bacteria"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.2,
    "endTime": 121.2,
    "text": "than a toilet seat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.2,
    "endTime": 124.56,
    "text": "like staphylococcus aureus which in some"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.56,
    "endTime": 127.68,
    "text": "rare cases can be deadly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.68,
    "endTime": 130.8,
    "text": "now on a slightly less or perhaps more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.8,
    "endTime": 133.84,
    "text": "frightening note dirty sheets can also"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.84,
    "endTime": 135.76,
    "text": "give you acne"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.76,
    "endTime": 138.8,
    "text": "each night the oil lotion and other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.8,
    "endTime": 141.12,
    "text": "cosmetics on your skin transfer to your"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.12,
    "endTime": 144.08,
    "text": "sheets and build up over time until"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.08,
    "endTime": 146.319,
    "text": "eventually your bedding is basically a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.319,
    "endTime": 149.04,
    "text": "giant used makeup wipe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.04,
    "endTime": 151.12,
    "text": "then during the following nights all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.12,
    "endTime": 154.239,
    "text": "that gunk transfers back onto your body"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.239,
    "endTime": 157.28,
    "text": "clogging your pores and voila"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.28,
    "endTime": 158.72,
    "text": "you've got acne"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.72,
    "endTime": 161.2,
    "text": "fortunately there's a simple way to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.2,
    "endTime": 163.08,
    "text": "avoid all of these problems"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.08,
    "endTime": 164.319,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.319,
    "endTime": 166.319,
    "text": "wash your sheets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.319,
    "endTime": 168.48,
    "text": "and wash them often"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.48,
    "endTime": 170.959,
    "text": "experts recommend about once a week"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.959,
    "endTime": 173.36,
    "text": "using the hottest water possible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.36,
    "endTime": 175.2,
    "text": "that'll kill a lot of bacteria and dust"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.2,
    "endTime": 178.4,
    "text": "mites get out stains and remove oils"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.4,
    "endTime": 180.64,
    "text": "plus as awful as making your bed might"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.64,
    "endTime": 181.76,
    "text": "be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.76,
    "endTime": 183.76,
    "text": "there's simply nothing better than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.76,
    "endTime": 189.159,
    "text": "slipping between clean crisp sheets"
  }
]